description: Try our easy to follow Barbecued Whole Barramundi With Fennel, Dill & Lemon Stuffing recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
keywords: Barbecued Whole Barramundi With Fennel, Dill & Lemon Stuffing
name: Barbecued Whole Barramundi With Fennel, Dill & Lemon Stuffing Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Heat a barbecue or chargrill over medium-high heat. Cook fish parcels for 10 minutes on each side and cook lemon slices for 1 minute. Serve fish topped with pickled fennel, lemon slices and remaining dill.
